\newlabel{fig:noise-stage}{{12}{18}{Stage-wise robustness under semantic tag dropout. The curves show how query formation, retrieval, target materialization, and post-retrieval completion change as dropout increases. Hazard recovery degrades early in the pipeline, while the resource tasks remain comparatively flat}{figure.12}{}}
